channel.title: Auto cache to user.home, only sends 4 files in my cache
channel.description: So I did everything right (i think) but when it auto sends my cache to my user.home, my client says Unable to download cache or whatever. So I check the cache in my user.home and theres only 4 files in it. Why does it only send 4 files in the cache?
